Package: urlshorteneR
Type: Package
Title: The R Wrapper for the Bit.ly, Goo.gl and is.gd URL shortening services, using OAUTH2 authentication.
Description: Allows using different URL shortening services, which also provide expanding and analytic functions. 
Version: 0.8.2
Date: 2015-10-20
